            <p>Bangladesh is one of the most important countries in the southern part of Asia and one of the most populous and densely populated countries in the world. It shares borders with India to its north, west, and eastern directions and Myanmar to its southeastern direction. The country is located on the shores of the Bay of Bengal. </p>
